==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonmetallic
<hw>Non`me*tal"lic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
metallic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Resembling, or possessing the
properties of, a nonmetal or metalloid; <as>as, sulphur is a
<ex>nonmetallic</ex> element</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nonmetamorphic</ent>⟦br⟧
